The     postgresql package includes the client programs and libraries that     you'll need to access a PostgreSQL DBMS server.  These PostgreSQL     client programs are programs that directly manipulate the internal     structure of PostgreSQL databases on a PostgreSQL server. These client     programs can be located on the same machine with the PostgreSQL     server, or may be on a remote machine which accesses a PostgreSQL     server over a network connection. This package contains the docs     in HTML for the whole package, as well as command-line utilities for     managing PostgreSQL databases on a PostgreSQL server.         If you want to manipulate a PostgreSQL database on a local or remote     PostgreSQL server, you need this package. You also need to install     this package if you're installing the postgresql-server package.
